Async Json Schema Validation Keywords (SVK)
Set async:true into the keyword object
const extend = {
  keywords: {
    checkUser: {
      async: true, // 
        simulateAsyncFindUserCall({ [field]: value })
          .then((items) => (items.length === 0)),
    },
  },
};

And set $async:true into the json-schema as well
const schema = {
  $async: true, // 

